Class VisualTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.Parent
        • javafx.scene.Group
          • io.github.mountainrange.mule.gameplay.javafx.VisualTile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tile, javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class VisualTile
extends javafx.scene.Group
implements Tile
    A tile which is drawn onto the screen. This tile is for use with the VisualGrid class, and JavaFX in general. As such, it extends the group object, so other JavaFX objects can be added to it as children.
